A. Photoshop
B. GitHub README files
C. Excel sheets
D. Databases

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: GitHub uses Markdown for documentation.

10. Why do developers use README.md?

A. To store passwords
B. To explain projects
C. To compile code
D. To run programs

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: README explains usage, installation, and contribution.

11. Markdown is preferred over Word because:

