20. AI should be treated as:

A. Authority
B. Replacement
C. Thinking partner
D. Compiler

✅ Answer: C
📘 Explanation: AI can make mistakes, so verify outputs.

21. First step in verification:

A. Trust AI
B. Ignore AI
C. Compare with known rules
D. Restart

✅ Answer: C
📘 Explanation: Always validate against your knowledge.

