A. Waste time
B. Improve understanding
C. Debug code
D. Test UI

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: Helps ensure correctness and clarity.

23. What should you do if AI says “correct”?

A. Accept immediately
B. Ignore
C. Test it yourself
D. Delete

✅ Answer: C
📘 Explanation: Always validate claims practically.

24. Cross-referencing means:

A. Ignoring results
B. Asking multiple AI tools
C. Writing code
D. Testing UI

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: Helps confirm correctness across sources.

